吉他中心发起倡议，更换在洛杉矶野火中丢失的乐器https://www.nme.com/news/music/guitar-center-offers-to-replace-instruments-lost-in-los-angeles-wildfires-3828262?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=guitar-center-offers-更换在洛杉矶野火中丢失的仪器Surej SinghMon, 13 Jan 2025 03:58:57 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3828262 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该零售商正在接受一次性拨款申请，为洛杉矶的音乐家和音乐节目更换乐器或装备</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guitar-center-offers-to-replace-instruments-lost-in-los-angeles-wildfires-3828262">吉他中心发起更换在洛杉矶野火中丢失的乐器的倡议</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/guitar-center@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐器零售商吉他中心宣布了一项新计划，将帮助受<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">洛杉矶野火</a>影响的音乐家更换他们的乐器或装备 - 了解更多信息如下。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">娱乐界对“令人心碎”的洛杉矶野火的反应</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周，洛杉矶的几个街区开始同时发生五场野火，迫使超过 18 万居民撤离——据<a href="https://edition.cnn.com/weather/live-news/los-angeles-wildfires-palisades-eaton-california-01-12-25/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>CNN</em></a>报道，最新统计显示 24 人确诊死亡，而<a href="https://apnews.com/article/los-angeles-wildfires-southern-california-c5826e0ab8db965cb2814132ff54ee6f" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>美联社</em></a>报道有 16 人失踪。</p><p>周末，吉他中心<a href="https://guitarcenterfoundation.org/fires/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">宣布了这项新计划</a>，该计划从即日起持续至 2 月 28 日。吉他中心及其吉他中心音乐基金会共同确认，他们将通过一项特别的计划来支持受洛杉矶火灾影响的音乐家和音乐节目。 - 时间补助，使他们能够更换被毁坏的仪器或装备。</p><p>为了有资格获得补助金，申请的音乐家和项目必须满足几个标准：他们必须位于洛杉矶，可能必须提供丢失或地址证明，并且必须建立一个申请账户。</p><p>为了符合资格，音乐课程必须归类为以下之一：学生制作音乐的校内音乐课程、非学校运营的课外音乐课程、提供音乐指导的社区音乐课程参加社区或音乐治疗项目，其中参与者积极创作音乐。</p><p>值得注意的是，这笔赠款不提供现金——相反，它只会更换仪器或装备。此外，每位申请人的上限为 1,500 美元。</p><p><a href="https://guitarcenterfoundation.org/fires/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">要了解更多信息或申请补助金，请访问此处</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEqprcMSfpI/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%